Garden Flag Display holds 12 garden stakes. Flags/stakes/hardware are not included with the display

Dimensions: 9"H x 24"W x 24"D

Wooden flag pole with anti wrap sleeve.

Dimensions: 60"L x 1" diameter

Don't be fooled by the compact size of this display - it holds a lot of retail dollars! FlagTrends™ Large and Garden Size Flags are the same length when in their packaging, which easily allows you to display all sizes of flags in a minimal amount of space. This display is so versatile and compact, it easily moves around to different areas of your retail space with the attached wheels. Holds up to $2,000.00 in retail, which could lead to $17, 500.00 in yearly retail sales!

Dimensions: 62.5"H x 33"W x 20"D

Our Large Flag display holds twice as much product as before! Display everything your customers need - flags, garden stakes, poles, and hardware - jam-packed in a sleek footprint of just 6 square feet! Simple to assemble, this display features sturdy metal construction and wheels for easy movability. You will love its versatility and how it will maximize sales in your store. Holds over $5,000 in retail, which could lead to $25,000 in yearly sales.
